              "grid": 4,
              "hasConfig": false,
              "controls": [
                {
                  "value": "<h2><a data-udi=\"umb://document/2034af5890894c269599623d112de8bd\" href=\"/{localLink:umb://document/2034af5890894c269599623d112de8bd}\" title=\"Fra tro til viden\">Fra tro til viden</a></h2>\n<p><span>Formålet med </span><em>Det Tredie Testamente</em><span> er at løfte livets store spørgsmål ud af troens tågedis, frem til selvoplevelse og sikker viden. Det er værkets grundlæggende tese, at livets mysterium kan forklares videnskabeligt.</span></p>\n<h2><a data-udi=\"umb://document/8b1923debc314d9581fbcd3fd93c8a1a\" href=\"/{localLink:umb://document/8b1923debc314d9581fbcd3fd93c8a1a}\" title=\"Artikler\">Udvalgte tekster</a></h2>\n<p>Læs artikler og udvalgte tekster af Martinus og download brochurer.</p>\n<h2 class=\"blue-header\">Videointerviews</h2>\n<p><em> Det Tredie Testamente</em> forklaret på:</p>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"font_8\"><span><a rel=\"noopener undefined\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2tMdYuTGqfk\" target=\"_blank\" data-content=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2tMdYuTGqfk\" data-type=\"external\">20 sekunder</a></span> </li>\n<li class=\"font_8\"><span class=\"wixGuard\">​</span><span><a rel=\"noopener undefined\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CjNnbkDcaRY\" target=\"_blank\" data-content=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CjNnbkDcaRY\" data-type=\"external\">5 minutter</a></span></li>\n<li class=\"font_8\"><span></span><span><a rel=\"noopener undefined\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i2vCKDi-9sE&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;list=PLGxDjdiWjROp9kjPLVHrc3WzGPZLtw4jV\" target=\"_blank\" data-content=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=i2vCKDi-9sE&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;list=PLGxDjdiWjROp9kjPLVHrc3WzGPZLtw4jV\" data-type=\"external\">15 minutter</a></span></li>\n<li class=\"font_8\"><span><a rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://vimeo.com/209931571\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"30 minuter\">30 minutter</a></span><span></span></li>\n</ul>",
